Package: linux-binary-7.0.13+deb14-arm64-di
Architecture: arm64
Section: debian-installer
Priority: standard
Package-Type: udeb
Build-Profiles: <!noudeb !pkg.linux.nokernel !pkg.linux.quick>
Provides: kernel-image, kernel-image-7.0.13+deb14-arm64-di
Depends: linux-base-7.0.13+deb14-arm64-di
Kernel-Version: 7.0.13+deb14-arm64
Description: Linux kernel image for the Debian installer
 This package contains the kernel image and core modules for the Debian
 installer boot images.  It does _not_ provide a usable kernel for your
 full Debian system.

